description: From the manufacturer Feel good dough - Nature (4x90gr) Feel good dough! The SES dough in four cheerful colours. Dough that makes you feel good! The dough is fully vegan, gluten free and super washable. It's bright and soft. And the resealable packaging keeps your dough good for longer. Finished playing with the dough? Scan the QR code on the packaging and find out what you can do with the packaging! The Feel good Nature dough comes in the earthy colours of green, light blue, orange and brown. Contents Light-blue play dough (90g) Orange play dough (90g) Green play dough (90g) Brown play dough (90g) Containers are re-usable and without small parts Very soft and does not dry out while playing Gluten free, safe to use and more
